@startuml form-definition-lifecycle
title Form Definition Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : Defined in UI / Payload

Draft --> Requested : Submitted for Vertical Approval
Requested --> Approved : Logic Verified by Subject Expert

state Approved {
  [*] --> Active
}

Active --> Restricted : Policy Review in Progress
Active --> Deprecated : New Version Pushed

Deprecated --> Archived : Data Frozen
@enduml
